text:
Lutheran Cemetery (old) showing a set of four views. In No. 1 the view is southeast from the elevated line of the B.M.T. and shows at the left background the water tower of the Montauk Water Company. Also shown in the background is Public School No. 91, south of Central Ave. between 68th and 69th Streets; No. 2 shows a more easterly view; No. 3 shows P.S. No. 67 in the background; No. 4 is an easterly view, showing the chapel in the background.

April 1925.
Views 2, 3 & 4: 1922.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
title: Cemeteries - Lutheran Cemetery (old) - Queens.
